Name: Blood Ball
Description: Spawns bloodballs that have normal speed, radius, damage and cooldown

Name: Fire Ball
Description: Summons fire balls that have low attack speed, long range and high damage. Also cannot attack at close range.

Name: Fire Ring
Description: Creates a ring of fire around the tower, which deals normal damage periodically in a small radius

Name: Charred earth
Description: Creates a —Åharred earth at a far distance beyond the minimum radius and cyclically deals damage in AOE. Has a long recharge time

Name: Blizzard
Description: Creates a blizzard at a far distance beyond the middle radius and cyclically deals damage in AOE. Has a long recharge time

Name: Frost Arrow
Description: Spawns ice arrows on a fast reload that deal minor damage at mid-range

Name: Frost Shield
Description: Spawns ice arrows on a fast reload that deal minor damage at mid-range

Name: Boomerang
Description: Spawns boomerang along a line that passes through enemies, dealing normal damage, has a few recharge and an middle range.

Name: Dark matter
Description: Spawns a dark strike at a long distance, has a long cooldown and very high damage.

Name: Hypnotic aura
Description: Creates a ring of dark energy around the tower, which causes enemies periodic sleep

Name: Multiattack
Description: Spawns several dark attacks at once with a medium cooldown in a short distance, causing normal damage

Name: Poison Arrow
Description: Spawns poisoned arrows over a long distance, has a normal reload speed and deals minor damage

Name: Poison darts
Description: Spawns poison darts over a long distance, has a very high reload speed and deals extremely low damage.

Name: Poison Gas
Description: Creates a gas cloud around the tower that periodically deals normal damage in a medium radius

Name: Rock throw
Description: Spawns a rock throw that deals significant damage at long range and has a long cooldown, and cannot attack at close range.

Name: Stone wall
Description: Creates a structure at a large distance beyond the minimum radius that blocks passage for a period of time.

Name: Silver Arrow
Description: Spawns silver arrows at normal range, has average damage and reload speed

Name: Silver Storm
Description: Spawns a storm, sending silverballs in all directions, which cause very high damage, have a long recharge time and a long distance

Name: Lancers
Description: Deals a preemptive spear strike to an enemy who is trying to attack a tower with a medium cooldown.

Name: Spikes Shield
Description: Creates a spikes  barrier around the tower that deals retaliatory damage to anyone who attacks it

Name: Around ball
Description: Spawns around tower
